Kung Fu Hustle

Year: 2004
Actors/Actresses: Stephen Chow, Danny Chan, Yuen Wah, Yuen Qiu, Eva Huang
Description: Kung Fu Hustle is a 2004 action comedy film directed, produced and written by Stephen Chow, who also stars in the lead role. The other producers were Chui Po-chu and Jeffrey Lau, and the screenplay was co-written with Huo Xin, Chan Man-keung, and Tsang Kan-cheung.

